<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Greenside</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/logo2.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding-bottom: 100px; /* Espaço reservado para o rodapé fixo */
        }
        header, footer {
            background-color: #079404;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .navbar-default {
            background-color: #079404;
            border-color: #079404;
        }
        .navbar-default .navbar-brand, 
        .navbar-default .navbar-nav > li > a {
            color: white;
        }
        .section_carrossel {
            margin: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .carousel-inner > .item > img {
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .section_servicos, .section_planos, .section_testemunhos, .section_contato {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .section_servicos {
            background-color: #eafaf1;
        }
        .section_planos {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .section_testemunhos {
            background-color: #eafaf1;
        }
        .section_contato {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        footer {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 1000;
    height: 92px; /* Ajuste a altura conforme necessário */
    padding: 10px 0; /* Ajuste o padding para compactar mais */
    background-color: #079404;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="navbar-header">
                    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                        <img alt="Greenside" src="/logoMain.png" style="height: 54px; width: 270px; margin-left: 35px; margin-top: -9px;">
                    </a>
                </div>
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/servicos">Serviços</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/planos">Planos</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contato">Contato     http://localhost:3002/erro-inexistente                     </a></li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li><a href="/user"><img src="/userIcon.svg" alt="Usuário" style="height: 42px;"></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="section_carrossel">
            <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="item active">
                        <img src="/img1.jpg" alt="Slide 1" style="width:80%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>Bem-vindo à Greenside</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="/img2.jpg" alt="Slide 2" style="width:80%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>Nossos Serviços</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="/img3.jpg" alt="Slide 3" style="width:80%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>Planos e Benefícios</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
                </a>
                <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section_servicos">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Nossos Serviços</h2>
                <p>Descrição dos serviços oferecidos pela clínica.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section_planos">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Nossos Planos</h2>
                <p>Descrição dos planos e benefícios.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section_testemunhos">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Testemunhos</h2>
                <p>O que nossos clientes estão dizendo:</p>
                <blockquote>
                    <p>"A Greenside transformou minha experiência de saúde."</p>
                    <footer>- Cliente Satisfeito</footer>
                </blockquote>
                <blockquote>
                    <p>"Serviço de primeira classe e profissionais dedicados."</p>
                    <footer>- Usuário Contente</footer>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section_contato">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contato</h2>
                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="nome">Nome:</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nome" placeholder="Seu nome">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Seu email">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="mensagem">Mensagem:</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="mensagem" rows="3" placeholder="Sua mensagem"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="/logoMain.png" alt="Logo Greenside">
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/servicos">Serviços</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/planos">Planos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contato">Contato</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-social">
                    <a href="#"><img src="/facebook-icon.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
                    <a href="#"><img src="/instagram-icon.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                    <a href="#"><img src="/linkedin-icon.png" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2025 Greenside. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
                <p><a href="#">Política de Privacidade</a> | <a href="#">Termos de Uso</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
